      • prepareRequest

        public String prepareRequest(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest req,
                             JSONObject serviceData,
                             JSONObject pathData,
                             List<FormattedMessage> messages)
                      throws IOException
        input has data received, except from header. validate and copy based on parameter specifications
        Parameters:
        req - request
        serviceData - non-null, into which all data is copied to. Typically this is an empty JSON, but it is upto the caller.
        pathData - can be null. field values from path templating.
        messages - non-null. Any error during parsing/validation is added to this list
        Returns:
        serviceName to be used for this operation. null in case of any error.
        Throws:
        IOException
